name: Netsky
description: '''Boris Daenen''' ({{IPA|nl|ˈboːrɪz ˈdaːnə(n)|lang}}; born 22 March 1989), better known by his stage name '''Netsky''' ({{IPAc-en|n|ɛ|t|ˈ|s|k|aɪ}} {{respell|net|SKY}}), is a Belgian [[drum and bass]] producer and musician. The name Netsky is based on the [[Netsky (computer worm)|computer virus of the same name]].
